Introduction

StelLive is a nine-member VTuber girl group under Accelers. The group consists of three subunits: the 1st Generation 'Mystic', the 2nd Generation 'Universe', and the 3rd Generation 'Cliché'. Though the members are Korean, they have all adopted Japanese stage names.

The group officially debuted on February 24, 2024, with their first single, "Milky Way."

On December 2, 2024, Airi Kanna graduated from the group.
